<TEXT PARTNO="005">
Knowing <COREF ID="17" TYPE="IDENT">New York</COREF> better than <COREF ID="48" TYPE="IDENT">Hualien</COREF>
<COREF ID="33" TYPE="IDENT">A city</COREF> can thrive or wilt in response to <COREF ID="67" TYPE="IDENT">political and economic changes to a nation</COREF> .
<COREF ID="67" TYPE="IDENT">These developments</COREF> can even slowly and silently change <COREF ID="33" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> basic character .
<COREF ID="77" TYPE="IDENT">Taipei 's</COREF> character is much different than those of other Taiwanese cities .
