<TEXT PARTNO="006">
Not losing face for <COREF ID="47" TYPE="IDENT">the nation</COREF>
" <COREF ID="48" TYPE="IDENT">Taipei</COREF> is under a lot of pressure because <COREF ID="48" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> faces international competition , " says <COREF ID="74" TYPE="IDENT">William Chen , the head of <COREF ID="48" TYPE="IDENT">Taipei 's</COREF> Bureau of Urban Development</COREF> .
